\pard\f0\fs28 Annual herbs. Leaves alternate, entire. Involucral bracts in several rows, very unequal, increasing in length inwards. Receptacle flat, alveolate. Florets yellow, the outer ligulate, female, the inner tubular, hermaphrodite. Achenes narrowly cylindrical, hairy; pappus of short scales and, in the inner achenes, a few long hairs, plumose in the distal third.
\par 
